{"tid":51319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公安拍片籲防「顏色革命」 驚現香港佔中畫面","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T08:07:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28d5932ba4346e235f9ab3c20b2c46e370657e25","tid":51319,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaj0NKwLGx0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Daaj0NKwLGx0&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YveYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=6f67baf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaj0NKwLGx0</a> <br />\n<br />\n特朗普當選美國總統後、中美關係陰霾重重之際，《聯合早報》等媒體報道，中國公安部「打四黑除四害專項行動辦公室」官方微博上周四發布短片，題為「誰最想扳倒（顛覆）中國」，其間點名美國；談及「境外勢力」及「顏色革命」時，還出現了香港佔中及其他示威衝突畫面，並點出本土派之名。 <br />\n<br />\n這部名為「誰最想扳倒中國」的短片，最先提到了被「顏色革命奪去家園」難民的悲慘遭遇，稱許多難民幾年前曾慶祝「阿拉伯之春」帶來了美麗的新世界，而現如今則生活在「廢墟、混亂、恐怖、絕望」之中。 <br />\n<br />\n其後短片中提到，「顏色革命已經成功讓許多國家陷入戰火和分裂，惡魔的利爪也伸向了中國」。此後短片中點名美國試圖對中國進行「和平演變」，並且通過在韓國部署「薩德」反導彈系統等方式，「多方面圖謀遏制中國」。 <br />\n<br />\n「誰最想扳倒中國」 點名美國 <br />\n<br />\n視頻中還出現了在香港爆發佔中及其他抗議活動的畫面，視頻中稱這些抗議活動「是民意的真實表達還是境外勢力攪局，事實真相令人警醒」！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1576935/12_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1576935%2F12_1024.png&h=1ad65943&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n短片中，出現了香港示威衝突的畫面。 <br />\n<br />\n短片還提到「境外勢力」利用「互聯網等傳播載體，否定中國歷史文化，培養顏色革命思想基礎」，並且把香港作為顏色革命的基地。短片最後強調，和平與穩定是「實現我們的復興之夢的首要保障」，提醒民眾不偏聽，不輕信，了解歷史，堅定信仰，抵禦顏色革命，要做到「若有戰，召必回」。 <br />\n<br />\n盡管共青團中央的官方微博轉發了這部短片，並提到了公安部「打四黑除四害專項行動辦公室」，但記者在後者的官方微博內，再沒有找到這部短片。"},{"pid":"4e0b49ae6504b613aad6e19013838e1e58f6169d","tid":51319,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T01:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0aa22f97d8c9b1c99a143b0d6e2852155d9d16","tid":51319,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5267e5f89e10498ed6efb6b1818ab3a2d26ec52","tid":51319,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"又宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc35f1ee896c7b0ea1bdea6741183b5b1e90d42","tid":51319,"uid":34319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"華夏文化劣根性最叻卸膊<br />\n乜勁都懶境外勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c17768bc4be115862e8e2ddd4452d9a51aac24","tid":51319,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f6d33d58af4c86fe71df45536c262d51192bb4","tid":51319,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"仲顏色革命<br />\nout晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c8c4c0c5a9c1e34e51581e9f4ab83bf46ebeb3","tid":51319,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲顏色革命<br />\nout晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n證明中國資訊落後歐美廿年"},{"pid":"ba8d69502046cdc085e0aabfa3c56db0e3c21e82","tid":51319,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:02:54.000Z","msg":"話唔定條片整足年幾"},{"pid":"d4a524c9ed6a94ba697bf600c61d5495af1b1eae","tid":51319,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}